  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Mix the mixed peel, gluten-free flour blend, baking powder, and salt in a large mixing bowl.",
    "Gradually add water while mixing until you get a stiff dough. Knead the dough for about 2 minutes on a floured surface.",
    "Place the dough into a lightly oiled pie dish and bake for 30-40 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Let it cool before serving with your favorite accompaniments."
